'''大力士高速列車槍擊案'''，是2015年8月21日發生在[[大力士高速列車|大力士高速列車]]上的槍擊案，該案發列車出發自[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]，經過[[比利時|比利時]][[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]，原本預定開往法國[[巴黎|巴黎]]，在行經[[瓦尼_(加來海峽省)|瓦尼]]時，列車內發生槍擊案，摩洛哥籍嫌犯Ayoub El-Kahzzani被两名正在休假的美国军人史賓瑟·史東和亞歷克·史卡拉托斯（史賓賽·史東来自[[美国空军|空军]]，史卡拉托斯来自[[奧勒岡州|奧勒岡州]][[國民警衛隊|國民警衛隊]]，在休假前派驻在阿富汗）和他们的朋友安東尼·薩德勒、同車英国乘客克里斯·諾曼與一位法国乘客制伏。之后列車緊急停靠在[[阿拉斯|阿拉斯]]。因嫌犯早已被歐洲反恐情報單位列為監控，[[夏尔·米歇尔|比利時首相]]稱此案為恐怖攻擊。<ref>{{cite news|title=法國火車發生槍擊 3人受傷槍手遭逮|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201508220007-1.aspx|accessdate=2015-08-23|agency=中央通訊社|archive-date=2015-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150822191136/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201508220007-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=法國高鐵險大屠殺！ 休假美軍勇擒槍手|url=http://udn.com/news/story/6809/1139235|accessdate=2015-08-23|agency=聯合新聞網|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125095405/https://udn.com/news/story/6809/1139235|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 涉及乘客 ==
*戴米安·A（Damien A.）：當年28歲的法國人，為第一位試圖對付槍手的乘客。事後，他希望保持著匿名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11819824/France-train-attack-Mark-Moogalian-named-as-French-hero-who-foiled-attack-by-Moroccan-terrorist-Ayoub-El-Khazzani-live.html |title=French hero's wife: 'He looked at me and said, 'I'm hit.' He thought he was going to die' – live |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |author=Raziye Akkoc |date=2015-08-24 |accessdate=2015-08-24 |quote=The 28-year-old French banker known only as "Damien A" was the first person to tackle the gunman, but does not want to be named |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211021927/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11819824/France-train-attack-Mark-Moogalian-named-as-French-hero-who-foiled-attack-by-Moroccan-terrorist-Ayoub-El-Khazzani-live.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*馬克·穆加利安（Mark Moogalian）：當年51歲的法國教師，他在美國出生，並擁有雙重國籍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/5th-paris-train-hero-id-french-american-professor-article-1.2335351|title=3 Americans and Brit honored in France as 5th train hero is identified as French-American professor|work=The New York Daily News|date=2015-08-26|accessdate=2015-08-26|first=Meg|last=Wagner|first2=Leonard|last2=Greene|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714213509/https://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/5th-paris-train-hero-id-french-american-professor-article-1.2335351|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在[[索邦學院|索邦學院]]教導英語。他試圖與槍手搏鬥。他在[[里耳|里耳]]遭受了一次非致命性的槍傷，並需要緊急手術<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/08/24/europe/france-train-shooting/index.html|title=Train heroes 'gave us an example of what is possible,' says French President|publisher=CNN|date=2015-08-25|accessdate=2015-08-25|first=Ralph|last=Ellis|first2=Faith|last2=Karimi|first3=Ashley|last3=Fantz|first4=Nic|last4=Robertson|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128114356/https://www.cnn.com/2015/08/24/europe/france-train-shooting/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*克里斯·諾曼（Chris Norman）：當年62歲的英國商人，他居住在法國<ref name="gdn Uganda">{{cite web | url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/aug/24/british-train-hero-chris-norman-receive-frances-highest-honour | title=French train attack heroes to be awarded Légion d’honneur | work=The Guardian | date=2015-08-24 | accessdate=2015-09-09 | archive-date=2020-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123114626/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/aug/24/british-train-hero-chris-norman-receive-frances-highest-honour | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也幫忙制服了槍手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://heavy.com/news/2015/08/chris-norman-belgium-france-paris-terrorist-train-attack-gunman-hero-morocco-skarlatos-anthony-sadler-video-photos-injured-medal-british-consultant/|title=Chris Norman, Belgium Train Hero: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know|work=Heavy|date=2015-08-22|accessdate=2015-09-03|first=Stephanie Dube|last=Dwilson|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919024816/https://heavy.com/news/2015/08/chris-norman-belgium-france-paris-terrorist-train-attack-gunman-hero-morocco-skarlatos-anthony-sadler-video-photos-injured-medal-british-consultant/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* [[安東尼·薩德勒|安東尼·薩德勒]]（Anthony Sadler）：當年23歲的[[加州州立大學薩克拉門托分校|加州州立大學薩克拉門托分校]]大四生，他是史東和史卡拉托斯的前高中同學。他與史東和斯卡拉托斯共同擊敗槍手。
* {{le|亞歷克·史卡拉托斯|Alek Skarlatos}}：當年22歲的{{le|俄勒岡陸軍國民警衛隊|Oregon Army National Guard}}下士，在[[阿富汗戰爭_(2001年)|阿富汗]]部署後到此度假。他和史東是前鄰居和同學。他持槍擊傷了槍手。
* {{le|史賓瑟·史東|Spencer Stone}}<ref name="sacbee.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.sacbee.com/news/local/article31991493.html|title=Carmichael childhood, faith unite friends who stopped train attack|work=The Sacramento Bee|date=2015-08-23|accessdate=2015-08-24|first=Hudson|last=Sangree|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207070336/https://www.sacbee.com/news/local/article31991493.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>：當年23歲的[[美國空軍|美國空軍]]{{le|空軍一等兵|Airman first class}}，隸屬於{{le|美國空軍第65基地聯隊|65th Air Base Group|第65基地聯隊}}，他利用休假來此遊玩。他在里耳附近的一家醫院接受了幾次割傷、手指骨折、右眼受傷的治療。他隨後前往德國[[拉姆施泰因空軍基地|拉姆施泰因空軍基地]]的一家醫院做進一步的治療<ref name="doing well">{{cite web | url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2015/08/25/airman-wounded-in-train-attack-being-treated-at-us-military-hospital-in-germany/ | title=Airman wounded in train attack being treated at US military hospital in Germany, doing well | agency=Associated Press | date=2015-08-25 | accessdate=2015-08-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828031642/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2015/08/25/airman-wounded-in-train-attack-being-treated-at-us-military-hospital-in-germany/ | archive-date=2015-08-28 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/france-train-attack-spencer-stone-gunman-was-ready-to-fight-but-so-were-we/|title=Hero American: Train attacker was ready to fight, but "so were we"|publisher=CBS News|date=2015-08-23|access-date=2015-08-31|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201125215/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/france-train-attack-spencer-stone-gunman-was-ready-to-fight-but-so-were-we/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory/american-recalls-french-train-attack-jimmy-fallon-show-33473492|title=California Man Recounts Tackling Gunman on Paris-Bound Train|publisher=ABC News|date=2015-09-02|accessdate=2015-09-03|first=Janie|last=Har|archive-date=2015-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904031544/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory/american-recalls-french-train-attack-jimmy-fallon-show-33473492|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
* 法國列車司機：他也幫忙制伏了槍手。他的名字至今仍未對外釋出。

== 影響 ==
2015年8月29日，歐洲多個國家經過會議研討後，開始規劃鐵路運輸的身份檢查、行李安檢與警察巡邏等安全措施。<ref>{{cite news|title=列車恐攻案　歐洲擬嚴檢身分和行李|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20150831/681207/|accessdate=2015-08-30|agency=蘋果日報|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304140224/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20150831/681207/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

